{"hb706a95dgb095g4c75g9c97gf11517e7d5ff": ["You think Arabella is scared - wherever she is? ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "7d2b5a3d-8ec1-9373-0dbe-245a5456d73c"], "hc5f6e247g2e95g4e7cgabcdg5d12131c9aa0": ["I think she's probably pickpocketed half of the Fugue Plane and is having a blast. ", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "14027ff0-a6f4-508d-c57d-a10a48ca2606"], "hd3b549eag2ef3g4bf3g9a3agf0f510eba915": ["Hah. I bet Kelemvor is fit to strangle her. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "f624f172-6261-9233-3c58-e5f00f8565ac"], "h84d2d995g413ag4eb0gae8ag52a3ab6f065a": ["He'll never catch her.", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "1c97cdfd-9dad-7a01-7e3a-645b9303fd37"], "hf65b6e5bg7e0fg4ab4ga194gff9c12146782": ["I want to see her. So much. ", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "09baaf70-8da9-fde1-d9b6-6632c6ed9940"], "h2a16bef5ge7feg4848g97eeg7154b11010db": ["We will. One day. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "a50b6a2b-e9cb-108f-f131-0119e9267433"], "ha84437e9g2abbg40fbgaa5cg5fbff006ba61": ["It doesn't feel right - going to Baldur's Gate without our little girl.", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "70c7ad63-7c19-428f-255c-42c7cc599154"], "hbfd0fdb1g6eebg41e6gb803g52db60880ef2": ["She was so looking forward to the city.", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "ddfd91e6-18ef-ee29-9ec1-f865ecd6e577"], "h574a04e8g1ee0g4c3egb750g5e374063fcb1": ["Yes, she hated being in the grove.", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "db097a46-b580-2743-817d-d63ae71c9965"], "h88973272ga3d0g49afg8284g8df3a21d1964": ["I wonder if she knew something was going to happen to her?", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "bdac90bb-14fe-a083-6a21-bd092e30941c"], "hf2e75d18g544eg4654ga393gc784d87c0616": ["I hope not. ", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "d3b9facb-4b50-6d60-7af7-ca28b59d8e6f"], "h431698e5gb9dag4fbbg8fa0g82b9ccf1a058": ["How're you holding up? ", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "a213eeb0-f951-0323-a742-b60e01505cd4"], "h7de73459gaa5fg4caag9c16g41cb8985b3eb": ["Fine. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "6d34af3f-292f-4488-651b-b6ca96f53cec"], "h5b7e9571g244ag4defg8c90gda88acdbcd48": ["Marri. ", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "ec6b4eea-00d1-2f49-8a39-ae91415c8706"], "h356aed24g7330g40d3g9cfbga350c878c64b": ["I'm not fine. Not one bit.", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "b6592fbe-e720-5af0-72c4-299cf410e6e1"], "heba72234gb6a4g4e21gad92geefb3979ea79": ["I thought killing that snake would make it hurt less.   ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "757f6855-0854-8c42-c3b0-869c2c39d4e6"], "h2ab543b9g237fg4999gadcbg29ca53ad1565": ["I just miss Arabella more. Why? Why did she have to die? ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "8fab40dd-e975-676c-e92a-4dd48dcc0243"], "h0f4af530gf2adg4c69g904agfcae7f83e0f6": ["I don't know. ", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "156cf989-c66f-b265-28dc-d49b6d64178f"], "hec2bf1e7g5a03g4ee3gb24cga9ef74016925": ["But Arabella saw justice. Because of you. ", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "3eb948fb-9eac-76f2-a83f-5374d6f7f185"], "h8c3fe366gd04eg4b4dg9a4cg3ee5f626976a": ["I killed someone, Locke. I stabbed them to death. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "c7bf1164-ad0e-474c-6a97-e511d61ea88f"], "h518dc9e2g6b35g4c2fga7e9ga1d37085719b": ["And I don't feel bad. You must think I'm a monster. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "56c5b660-7c91-9dce-97bb-40d7347e63b8"], "hd700fe16g3d6eg4931gb8f4g6bdd92c7c21e": ["No. I'm <i>proud </i>of you. I know Arabella would be too. ", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "fa2bf9fe-a8db-8a85-8c89-a87531926b8f"], "hd06374f2g27b4g4114g9dffgf1e16bd535a8": ["You two fought noon and night, but there's no one she looked up to more. ", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAlone.html", "fc1368d5-a41f-a752-a441-da1a1982787e"]}